PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of Ronald E. Lawless, of Beaconsfield, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company for a term of one year; and re-appointment of the said Ronald E. Lawless as President and Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, effective October 1, 1990.
